        "TileImage": "$($repository 5c9a59eb-7dc4-4785-983f-7e411a755bab).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening, 47. Your destination is the private yacht belonging to infamous cat burglar Kalvin Ritter, a.k.a The Sparrow.\r\rYour target is Lukas Fnullman, the captain of the yacht who secretly plans to sink the boat in the open ocean - with everyone stil inside. You also have to eliminate Terry Norfolk, a very well-dressed gentleman who is Fnullman&apos;s assistant in the operation.\r\rWe have a possible terrorist attack on the horizon, 47. This cannot come to pass.\r\rI will leave you to prepare.",
